::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe shakes his head. "No that will be all."

Suddenly, the assassin flips out a pistol, aiming behind him and 
firing at the cave entrance. The shot explodes as it hits, starting a 
cave in, rocks falling to block the entrance to the cave, atleast 
that entrance.

"I don't believe I've thanked you for your hospitality," DeathScythe 
snarls, firing the same weapon at Zyber. His eyes were blood red 
again, his whole manner that of a mercyless killer.
